as instruments today. Avedis Zildjian [zil-jin] worked in this country, the setting of an opera in which
Belmont rescues Konstanze from Pasha Selim. Western orchestras imported the triangle, bass drum, and
cymbals from this country, the setting of Mozart’s Abduction from the Seraglio. For the point, a craze for
what country’s music was inspired by the Janissary military bands?=====
